## Completeness Checklist

- [ ] Phase transition fields correctly populated
- [ ] Summary accurately reflects state of project at handover point
- [ ] All artefacts from {{from_phase}} listed with location and status
- [ ] Open risks transferred with current score and mitigation status
- [ ] Open assumptions transferred with validation deadlines
- [ ] Open clarifications transferred with deadlines
- [ ] Technical briefing notes sufficient for incoming team to continue without knowledge loss
- [ ] Operational constraints and warnings documented
- [ ] Gate status recorded and gate has been formally closed (or waived)
- [ ] Formal sign-off obtained from all three parties

